{"id":1101,"date":"2024-08-02T23:56:48","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T23:56:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1101"},"modified":"2024-08-02T23:56:48","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T23:56:48","slug":"tm103-sludge-wave","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm103-sludge-wave\/","title":{"rendered":"TM103 Sludge Wave"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM103 Sludge Wave<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>At the Battle Tower TM counter for 48 Battle Points.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>The area around the user is swamped by a giant sludge wave. It may also poison those hit.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Poison<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat the Champion at least once to unlock the Battle Frontier<\/li>\n<li>Have at least 48 Battle Points<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Seaport City Pok\u00e9mon Center after defeating the Champion at least once and enter the connector to your North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-connector-in-seaport-city.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the connector in Seaport City. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the connector in Seaport City.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue North to exit the connector from the other side.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-exiting-the-connector-from-the-other-side.jpg\" alt=\"Exiting the connector from the other side. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exiting the connector from the other side.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After exiting the connector, you want to keep running North.<\/p>\n<p>Eventually you\u2019ll enter the main Battle Tower.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-battle-tower.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Battle Tower. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Battle Tower.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside, head to the counter to your East where you\u2019ll see three receptionists. Interact with the bottom-most one.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-speaking-with-the-receptionist-who-provides-tms.jpg\" alt=\"Speaking with the receptionist who provides TMs. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Speaking with the receptionist who provides TMs.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then select the TM for Sludge Wave and redeem it for 48 Battle Points.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-acquiring-the-sludge-wave-tm-for-48-battle-points.jpg\" alt=\"Acquiring the Sludge Wave TM for 48 Battle Points. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Acquiring the Sludge Wave TM for 48 Battle Points.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1102,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-1101","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1101","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1102"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1101"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1101"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}